The paper deals with the problem of optimal user assignment to antenna domains in cloud radio access networks, which is a problem in wireless communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves optimization and algorithmic aspects, which suggest the categories cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions numerical results, which suggest the categories cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
